    You can use <code>dashArray</code>, <code>width</code>, and <code>fill</code> properties to customize the line. <code>marker</code> and <code>dataLabel</code> are used to represent individual data and its value.
</p>
<p>
    Tooltip is enabled in this example. To see the tooltip in action, hover a point or tap on a point in touch enabled devices.
</p>
